name: 2 Bundle Special Brazilian 12"-22"
description:
Brazilian hair is the most versatile and unique as the textures and colors vary tremendously. The hair is 100% virgin meaning that it has absolutely no treatment nor processing. 
 
Hair comes in natural color. Or you have the option to dye hair the color you desire
Hair has little to No shedding and tangling, TOP QUALITY!!!
Hair can be straightened, curled or styled to your desire
Hair can last up to a year or more with proper care

**SPECIAL INCLUDES ANY 2 BUNDLES BETWEEN 12"-22" INCHES PLEASE SPECIFY IN THE NOTE BOX AT CHECKOUT OR IN THE CONTACT BOX, WHAT "2 INCHES" YOU WOULD LIKE YOUR BUNDLES IN, IF YOU DO NOT CONTACT US IT MAY TAKE LONGER TO PROCESS YOUR ORDER***

Note: Once hair is colored it is no longer considered "100% VIRGIN" because it has now been through a processing stage.
